English:
//HearSay auto-transcript begins// 
 
GARGANTA ALERT SYSTEM 
All personnel clear the operations floor. All personnel clear the operations floor. 
 
STOKES 
Settle down everyone!  I need final checks from all systems. Telemetry? 
 
VOICE 2 
Online. 
 
STOKES 
Wave stabilizers? 
 
VOICE 3 
Check. 
 
STOKES 
Temporal regulators? 
 
VOICE 4  
Good to go. 
 
STOKES 
Quantum tethering?

Secured and locked. 
 
STOKES 
Frequency modulation?

Low standard deviation... we are good to go. 
 
STOKES 
Mission team? 
 
BISHOP 
BIOCOM command, this Security Operative Bishop requesting E-F-Zero One clearance. Clearance has been granted. E-F-Zero One is operational. You may proceed Dr. Stokes. 
 
STOKES 
Thank you, Sergeant. Chrono, start the mission clock. 
 
VOICE 2 
Clock is running. 
 
STOKES 
Good luck everyone. 
 
GARGANTA ALERT SYSTEM 
Translocational jump sequence... initiated. 
 
VOICE 2 
The gate is open! 
 
VOICE 3 
Matter wave capacitors at forty percent! 
 
VOICE 2 
Chrono is slowing down doctor! Should we 
 
STOKES 
No! Keep going! 
 
VOICE 3 
Matter wave capacitors at eighty percent! 
 
STOKES 
Bishop! Keep everyone within the projection radius! 
 
VOICE 3 
Chrono has stopped! I'm getting no temporal progression! 
 
VOICE 4 
Quantum tether is holding! 
 
VOICE 3 
Matter wave capacitors are primed! Ready to discharge! 
 
STOKES 
This is it. Go! Comms? 
 
VOICE 2 
Searching... 
 
STOKES 
Telemetry? 
 
VOICE 3 
Nothing. 
 
STOKES 
Did we lose the frequency? 
 
VOICE 4 
I've got no signal. 
 
STOKES 
Widen the scope. 
 
VOICE 4 
It's at full. 
 
STOKES 
Damn it! Comms? 
 
VOICE 2 
Nothing. 
 
STOKES 
God damn it! Power down. All departments. Briefing room, NOW! 

//HearSay auto-transcript ends//
